    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "but that's just fixing a machine that doesn't even want to run anymore. if the art is gone, the essence is gone. why should the physical part keep going just to go through the motions? it feels like I'm just preserving a corpse that hasn't stopped breathing yet.",
